{"tid":2249172,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港電台：台方人員挑釁執行公務的中國人員","createTime":"2020-10-19T07:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T07:55:07.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"remark":"[gold]⚠️ 管理團隊警示：本主題已被回報為「標題真實性有待確定，可能含有誤導或虛假資訊」，請各位留意。[/gold]\n警示措拖說明：https://lih.kg/eobQbT","replies":[{"pid":"7f0e6da3e42214c934a835db2cdf62edb2b8c216","tid":2249172,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:07:46.000Z","msg":"中國駐斐濟大使館表示，注意到一些社交媒體報道指，台北駐斐濟貿易辦事處本月8日在當地一間酒店舉辦的活動會場外發生的事情，當中有關中國使館工作人員的說法與事實完全不符。<br />\n<br />\n大使館表示，台方工作人員挑釁在活動場地外公共區域執行公務的中國駐斐濟使館工作人員，造成1名中國外交官受傷。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，台灣傳媒報道，兩名中國駐斐濟大使館的外交官當時闖入台灣駐斐濟代表處舉辦的雙十慶典活動現場，並且動手打人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555530-20201019.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555530-20201019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=efaa55a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555530-20201019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=75775247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555530-20201019.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"383433ef0f5aa0c94516fdb188d4d4d5dc0e365e","tid":2249172,"uid":50386,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"人哋響場內搞慶典，<br />\n班支那畜搞乜春公務呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9896a97e8ac34a0180526456e97fd64fa25751b5","tid":2249172,"uid":346701,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"係RTHK定支那駐斐濟大使館表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46da78a011a2e40d8743b8cb3f68f1065ce1bef6","tid":2249172,"uid":60694,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"On9仔你開post 同作新聞Fake news 有咩分別"},{